This guide will help you update a Partner's information.

{% include "alert/note", content: "Currently, you can only update a Partner's name. We will extend this tutorial with additional instructions once you can update other fields, too." %}

## Requirements
To follow the steps in this tutorial, you should be able to log in to the Partner Portal, and have access to a Partner (e.g. the Partner your User is assigned to).

* [Register on the Partner Portal](/get-started/hello-world/register-partner-portal)

## Steps

Updating a Partner is a two-step process:

<div data-autosteps></div>

### Step 1: Locate Partner

In the menu on the left, click on `Partners`, and select the Partner you would like to update. The information page of the Partner is displayed.

### Step 2: Update Partner

To update the Partner, click on `Edit`:

* `Name`: Edit the name of the Partner.

Click on `Update`. A `Partner was successfully updated.` message is displayed, and you can see that the information you edited has changed.

## Next steps
Congratulations! You have updated a Partner's information. Now you can learn about updating an Instance:

